this is the simple enviorment variable adding instead of downloading perfectly all the mongodb stuff
sometimes we cannot run commands like mongod --version or mongoimport/export on windows this can be solved using 
Go to "System Properties" > "Advanced" > "Environment Variables."
1->C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\7.0\bin  , 2->C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Tools\100\bin   (solution for windows 10/above  users)
